is_int <- function(x) abs(round(x)-x)<1.0e-4
is_square <- function(x) is_int(sqrt(x))
is_tria <- function(x) is_int(uniroot(function(n) n*(n+1)-2*x, c(0,x))$root)
n <- 37
while(!(is_tria(n) && is_square(n))) n <- n+1
n # 1225
